The best way to spend an afternoon ❤️ Yesterday we helped pack Mother’s Day gifts, baby care packages, fresh bouquets and more with @baby2baby. 

#Baby2Baby provides the basic essentials to children in homeless shelters, domestic violence programs, foster care, hospitals and underserved schools across the country as well as children who have lost everything in the wake of disaster.

In the last 12 years, Baby2Baby has distributed over 300 million essential items to children living in poverty across the country. Baby2Baby is not just for babies, they serve 1 million+ children annually ages 0-12 in every state.
Such a great event for an even better cause!! ❤️ @baby2baby 💐 #MothersDay

I can’t believe we’re writing this but our little girl is FOUR!! Where does the time go? 4 years ago today Madison Jade Mizanin came into this world and has been changing our lives ever since.  One minute she’s crawling and can’t speak, the next she walks, talks, dances, sings her ABC’s, makes decisions, tells us what to do (in the cutest way possible) and everyday finds new ways to make us proud and amaze us. I mean what 4-year-old’s favorite song is “Danger Zone” but has never seen “Top Gun?”She keeps us on our toes and we wouldn’t have it any other way.  We can’t wait to see what this next year brings and how she will continue to grow as our beautiful little girl. We love you.  Happy Birthday Madison!
